Klopp on Coutinho &amp; Firmino: &quot;At Leicester there were a lot of bad individual performances. So many not at their usual level.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;It's Anfield, our stadium and the last game we played there was fantastic. We want that feeling again.&quot;

Klopp: &quot;It's not being passive. It starts with a set-piece, long ball, Jamie Vardy, header, long ball, foul on Sadio, throw in to them.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;They felt immediately in this moment 'yes, that's what we want'. And obviously, we felt the opposite.&quot;
